## Conclusion

If you can see this page with proper USWDS styling, mdsvex is working correctly! The integration includes:

- ✓ Markdown processing via mdsvex
- ✓ USWDS prose typography
- ✓ Custom HTML element replacements
- ✓ Svelte component support
- ✓ Frontmatter metadata
- ✓ Code syntax highlighting
